title: MSACS Recruitment 2025 - Apply Offline for 02 Staff Nurse Posts
description: The Maharashtra State AIDS Control Society (MSACS) has declared the official notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 02 Staff Nurse Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the B.Sc Nursing, GNM can grab this chance and apply for the MSACS Recruitment 2025 . Here, we mentioned the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts.
